{
  "texts": [
    "➁ Fine-Tuning: a general domain language model is fine-tuned on all recipes from RecipeNLG.",
    "This model is further fine-tuned on the regression task to predict the stars from RELEXset.",
    "We call this fine-tuned model RELEXset-predictor.",
    "➂ Recipe Annotation: the recipies from RELEXset are annotated using writing suggestions obtained from experts.",
    "We denote the resulting dataset of annotated, rated recipes as RELEX-sugg-set."
  ]
}